♪Her heart has changed♪

164
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:47,400
♪I'm no longer in it♪

165
00:08:48,190 --> 00:08:51,660
♪Hugging myself under the streetlight♪

166
00:08:51,660 --> 00:08:54,550
♪That timidity♪

167
00:08:56,450 --> 00:09:01,060
♪Actually, I'm not that easy to deceive♪

168
