♪Why take advantage of my pity♪

170
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:10,340
♪And give me more memories♪

171
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:13,030
♪You didn't hear♪

172
00:09:13,530 --> 00:09:16,630
♪My last goodbye♪

173
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:20,770
♪I walked away♪

174
00:09:20,770 --> 00:09:24,100
♪With tears in my eye♪

175
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:28,260
♪Actually, you have changed too♪

176
00:09:28,470 --> 00:09:30,870
♪You just love him a little more♪

177
